<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Upload Selfie - ProFace AI</title>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<style>

body{
font-family:Arial;
background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f172a,#111827,#1e1b4b);
color:white;
margin:0;
text-align:center;
}

.container{
max-width:900px;
margin:auto;
padding:80px 20px;
}

h1{
font-size:42px;
margin-bottom:10px;
}

p{
color:#d1d5db;
}

.upload-box{
margin-top:40px;
padding:60px;
border:2px dashed rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
border-radius:20px;
background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
}

input{
margin-top:20px;
}

button{
margin-top:30px;
padding:14px 28px;
border:none;
border-radius:12px;
background:white;
color:black;
font-weight:bold;
cursor:pointer;
}

.tip{
margin-top:40px;
color:#9ca3af;
font-size:14px;
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

<h1>Upload ton selfie</h1>

<p>Ajoute 1 à 5 selfies pour générer ta photo LinkedIn professionnelle</p>

<div class="upload-box">

<input type="file" multiple>

<br>

<button>Générer mes photos</button>

</div>

<div class="tip">

✔ visage visible  
✔ bonne lumière  
✔ angle naturel  

</div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
